      %h5 A Common-Sense Guide to Data Structures and Algorithms
      %p A Common-Sense Guide to Data Structures and Algorithms is a technical text covering different data structures and methods for using them. The book goes over sorting techniques, how to use recursion, and specialized structures (such as graphs and trees). I provided didactic illustrations, the book was written by Jay Wengrow. Illustrated with Adobe Illustrator.
