      %h5 EIN/Tax ID Verification API
      %p A free service to verify non-profit organizations based on EIN or Tax ID. The API downloads and parses the latest tax-exemption lists from the IRS, then compares the given Tax ID number with the list's records for verification. Built with Ruby and Roda.
